    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu </p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 7</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 8</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 23 | <b>Successes:</b> 5</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 11 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 27</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>This technique is an effective way of countering opponents who use summoning techniques. If hit, the target must make a save or be immediately banished as though its duration had ended. Objects are not allowed a save. If a banished creature is Unique, Elite or Paragon, it cannot be summoned again for 1 day.</p>\n\n\n\n",
